    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this reliable ride. It\u2019s been such a solid car for me and is still in really nice shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable daily driver without the new-car price tag. It runs great and has been well-loved! I'm happy to answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out. Can't wait to see it go to a great new owner!",
