    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This unit is well-sorted, with documented rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements already performed. The powerplant's individual throttle bodies deliver immediate response up to the 8,400 RPM redline, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures precise torque vectoring across the rear axle. The chassis remains tight with no subframe issues, retaining the communicative hydraulic steering that defines this era of M-cars. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are dialed in for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained. Runs well. Clean interior and exterior. No major issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
