    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the perfect balance of luxury and reliability, meticulously maintained and ready for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the minor, expected signs of road use that come with a well-loved car. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin featuring supple leather seating with minimal wear and a full suite of fully operational electronic features, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has a documented history of on-time oil changes, a recent brake pad replacement, and tires with plenty of tread remaining. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts effortlessly, providing a quiet and confident ride. This is a solid, honest vehicle that looks great in any driveway and performs beautifully on the open road.",
      "price": 36500.0,
