      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional mechanical integrity and refined aesthetic appeal. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to a high standard, ensuring a driving experience that balances performance with proven reliability. Every component reflects a commitment to quality, offering the discerning buyer a premium asset at a competitive valuation. We invite you to experience a vehicle that exemplifies the intersection of durability and sophisticated design.",
