    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained. Perfect for weekend getaways or just zipping around town! It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin, I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
