      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains composed with recent bushing refreshes and documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. While the exterior shows minor patina indicative of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals\u2014including valve clearances and rod bearing service\u2014are up to date. This is a mechanically sound example that delivers the visceral, analog feedback characteristic of BMW\u2019s finest era.",
